<item>
            <title>[SPARK-14580] HiveTypeCoercion.IfCoercion should preserve original predicates.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-14580</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, `HiveTypeCoercion.IfCoercion` removes all predicates whose return-type is null. However, some UDFs need evaluations because they are designed to throw exceptions.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Hive&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;hive&amp;gt; select &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;(assert_true(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;),2,3);
OK
Failed with exception java.io.IOException:org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.metadata.HiveException: ASSERT_TRUE(): assertion failed.
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Spark&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;scala&amp;gt; sql(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;select &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;(assert_true(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;),2,3)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).head
res2: org.apache.spark.sql.Row = [3]
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;`IfCoercion` works like the followings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;=== Applying Rule org.apache.spark.sql.catalyst.analysis.HiveTypeCoercion$IfCoercion ===
!&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;Project [unresolvedalias(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (HiveGenericUDF#org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.udf.&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;generic&lt;/span&gt;.GenericUDFAssertTrue(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;)) 2 &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; 3)]   &apos;&lt;/span&gt;Project [unresolvedalias(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (nu
ll) 2 &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; 3)]
 +- OneRowRelation$                                                                                                           +- OneRowRelation$      
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue aims to fix this and to add `assert_true` as a Spark SQL function.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
